questions.quote: Joey, what are you doing? You promised Phoebe you wouldn't eat meat until she has the babies!
I, I don't know, um, do you think you're cute? OK, we're kinda gettin' off the track here. Um, I was supposed to come here and tell you my friend thinks you're cute. So what should I tell her?
Let me see, I gotta see, I gotta see. Oh, a head. Oh, it's, it's huge. Carol, how are you doing this?
I'm not really here. Just thought I'd drop these off...on the way.. my way... Do you come here a lot? Without me?
Okay Ben, why don't you come open some more presents, and Santa, the Armadillo, and I have a little talk in the kitchen? There's a sentence, I never thought I'd say.
Listen, Joey, I know what he did was wrong but don't you think you could at least hear the guy out?
Oh, I just thought we could go out to dinner, and then maybe bring her back to my place and I'd introduce her to my monkey.
Where'd you get too? We lost you after you opened up all the presents.
Maybe I could give thanks by taking my Playstation over to my new apartment.
Hey, Rach. How was it with your friends? Okay! How would you like some Tiki Death Punch?
